# Прямые $AB$ и $АС$ касаются окружности с центром $О$ в точках $В$ и $С$. Найдите $ВС$, если $\angle OAB = 30^\circ$, $AB = 5$ см.
scene "Two tangents from A to circle O; ∠OAB=30°, AB=5; find BC"
layout canonical=generic scale=1
points A, B, C, O

# Circle and tangent at B
circle center O radius-through B
line A-B tangent to circle center O at B

# The second tangent from A touches at C
line A-C tangent to circle center O at C

# Given data
angle O-A-B [degrees=30]
segment A-B [length=5, label="5"]

# Target: distance between touchpoints
target length B-C [label="?"]
